OL,3,CCumbrian man embarks on virtual cycle
OL,4,Cto Mars in memory of his wife and
OL,5,Cdaughter
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Gerard said:
OL,8,F"I have done two previous challenges
OL,9,Fwhere I cycled the heights of the four
OL,10,Fhighest peaks in England, Ireland,
OL,11,FScotland and Wales and then I went
OL,12,Fonto a second challenge which was to
OL,13,Fclimb the height of the highest
OL,14,Fmountain on earth.
OL,16,F"So when I came to do this challenge I
OL,17,Fthought I have to find something
OL,18,Fdifferent."
