OL,4,Cto Mars in memory of his wife and
OL,5,Cdaughter
OL,7,FGerard's wife died after a long fight
OL,8,Fwith Bronchiectasis and endured sight
OL,9,Floss for 40 years and his daughter
OL,10,Fdied from breast cancer in August this
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FHe is raising funds in their memory
OL,14,Fand spoke about why one the charities
OL,15,Fmeans so much to him.
OL,17,FHe said: "Hospice at Home is one of
OL,18,Fthose charities where people really
OL,19,Fcome to rely on them when it comes to
OL,20,Fserious illness.
